    .spotlightWrapper
        .content
            .cell
                .title Nashor's Tooth
                p
                    | Before the AP item change patch (5.13), there was a limited number of viable carriers for Nashor's Tooth.
                    | Is this still the case or have the changes to the item opened up more variety? Has this
                    | item found its own niche?
                blockquote
                    | [W]hile it's always been a great pickup for auto-attacking mages, that attack speed to ability power ratio meant you had to be pretty invested in your on-hit procs to even consider the Tooth. We're hoping this change will make it a little more enticing as a niche pickup for people not... Kayle.
                    cite
                        | Riot in
                        a(href='http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/game-updates/patch/patch-513-notes') Patch 5.13 Notes
            .cell
                center
                    img(src='http://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/5.2.1/img/item/3115.png')
                table.table.table-condensed
                    tr
                        td Pick Rate
                        td
                            | {{ nashor['pickDiff'] }}
                            i.glyphicon(ng-class="{'glyphicon-menu-up green': nashor['pickDiff'] > 0, 'glyphicon glyphicon-menu-down red': nashor['pickDiff'] < 0}")
                        td from
                        td {{ nashor['pickRate'] }}
                    tr
                        td Number of wins
                        td
                            | {{ nashor['winDiff'] }}
                            i.glyphicon(ng-class="{'glyphicon-menu-up green': nashor['winDiff'] > 0, 'glyphicon glyphicon-menu-down red': nashor['winDiff'] < 0}")
                        td from
                        td {{ nashor['winner'] }}
